Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, March 10 (KCNA) -- A meeting was held 
here Wednesday under the sponsorship of the Korea-Mauritius 
Friendship Association on the occasion of the 26th anniversary 
of the independence of Mauritius and the 2d anniversary of the 
proclamation of the republic. 
  Present at the meeting were Yi Chol-sin, vice-chairman of 
the 
Committee for Cultural Relations With Foreign Countries and 
vice-chairman of the Korea-Mauritius Friendship Association, and 
officials concerned and working people in the city. 
  A speech was made and a message of greetings to the 
president 
and the prime minister of Mauritius was adopted. 

